-- Pound Weakens Against Euro, Dollar as BOE Reviews Rate-Cut Case
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-07-18T08:35:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-18/pound-weakens-against-euro-dollar-as-boe-reviews-rate-cut-case.html
The pound weakened against the euro
and the dollar after  Bank of England  policy makers said they may
reconsider the case for an interest-rate cut after assessing the
impact of new measures on the economy.  The pound dropped 0.3 percent to $1.5615 at 9:35 a.m.
London time and weakened 0.2 percent to 78.67 pence per euro.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
